<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="MTA8">
<l>mayaṅka valampuri vāyvaittu vāṉat</l>
<l>tiyaṅku meṟikatirōṉ ṟaṉṉai – muyaṅkamaruṭ</l>
<l>ṭērāḻi yāṉmaṟaitta teṉṉī tirumālē</l>
<l>pōrāḻik kaiyāṟ porutu</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>In order to confuse [the enemy], putting the right-spiralling conch to [your] mouth,</l>
<l>why did you, Tirumāl, hide with a chariot wheel in [all]-encompassing</l>
<l>battle the [sun] with attacking rays that moves along the sky,</l>
<l>fighting with [your] hand [holding] the battle discus?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
